    ],
    "didYouKnow": [
      "The concept of Significant Figures was developed to prevent scientists from claiming false precision in their data."
    ],
    "summary": [
      "We classified matter and learned that every measurement has uncertainty, which we express using significant figures."
    ],
    "quickRevision": [
      "Remember: Leading zeros = No. Trailing with decimal = Yes."
